short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: IMPOSTOR.IO is a new game that's taking the world by storm. anticipate your opponents' actions, and dominate the server.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Impostor.io unbloked is available in the chrome web store just install it and play Impostor.io unbloked gme.


Enjoy this fun game where you must try to place yourself at the top of the leaderboard. You will have to fight against hundreds of adversaries from all over the world, it will be your life or theirs, so do not leave any of them alive. Every time you kill an opponent you will accumulate points. Go around the entire stage with great caution, nowhere will you be safe. You can change the color and appearance of your character. Collect energy cubes to level up and end up being stronger.

Note: There are more games available to play.

thank you:-)
